    "description": [
        {
            "@value": "A Welsh language religious periodical serving the Unitarians. The periodical's main contents were religious articles, domestic and foreign news and poetry. Originally a monthly publication it was published irregularly between 1969 and 1986, and bimonthly from 1987 onwards. Amongst the periodical's editors were the minister and schoolmaster, John Edward Jones (1801-1866), Thomas Arthur Thomas and David Jacob Davies. Associated titles: Yr Ymofynnydd (1926).",
            "@language": "en"
        },
        {
            "@value": "Cylchgrawn crefyddol, ar gyfer yr Undodiaid. Prif gynnwys y cylchgrawn oedd erthyglau crefyddol, newyddion cartref a tramor a barddoniaeth. Yn wreiddiol yn gylchgrawn misol gafodd ei chyhoeddi'n afreolaidd rhwng 1969 a 1986 ac yn daufisol o 1987 ymlaen. Ymhlith golygyddion y cylchgrawn oedd y gweinidog ac ysgolfeistr, John Edward Jones (1801-1866), Thomas Arthur Thomas a David Jacob Davies. Teitlau cysylltiol: Yr Ymofynnydd (1926).",
            "@language": "cy-GB"
        }
    ],
